{"id": "1392075768280125561", "channel_id": "1392075768280125561", "type": 0, "author_id": "139343733714845697", "author_name": "satachan", "author_bot": false, "content": "I have recieved the merchandise from the event giveaway and I am very happy to have the chance to recieve the items. \n\nHowever because I love morimens and its content, I would like to give my general feedback on it. \n\nThe quality and feel of the print is very good. \nIt is very well worth its price in terms of material quality. I can see this being in an album or in a case for showing.\n\nMy biggest problem is that the colors printed are generally too dark.  I believe this is due to the heavy holographic rarity effect shown on the cards. I think that it reduces the original color of the art work a little too much and it feel desaturated/overly contrasted\n\nThe matte texture on the card also reflects a lot of light when held up close so it is very hard to get a clear look at the details/colors \n\nI think all of this can be fixed by just making the illustration colors a little brighter. Or lowering the reflectivity of the material surface. \n\nThank you morimens for giving us players the chance to carry mythag around with us. \nI am very grateful!", "timestamp": "2025-07-08T09:32:06.675000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "pray", "emoji_id": "1356053116260454534", "count": 6}, {"emoji": "wow", "emoji_id": "1356053147029864518", "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1392075768955142184", "filename": "20250708_161403.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 818007, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1392075768280125561/1392075768955142184/20250708_161403.jpg?ex=69cc3d56&is=69caebd6&hm=8e2219127ec3181666ce5065dfe5fa027c7300ad23531cee97968fefa11e9f8a&"}, {"id": "1392075769534218302", "filename": "20250708_161433.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 998686, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/139207576828012